  "text": "Moto G Play (2024) $110 $150 Save $40 This phone scored pretty high in your review, delivering everything that you'd want from a phone at a great price. Right now, you can grab it for less, as it drops to just $110. It's easy to get a phone that's packed with features if you're willing to spend a lot of money. But if you're looking for something on a smaller budget, that's when it becomes a little harder to find a phone that checks all the boxes. Of course, that doesn't mean there aren't great options. Related The Moto G Play is one such example, delivering everything you'd want from a smartphone, packing tons of features, coming in at just $150. The best part is that it can sometimes be found on sale, like it is right now, with a small discount that brings it down to just $110. This is an excellent budget Android handset, so get it now for cheap while you can. What's great about the Moto G Play 2024? When it comes to the design, there's nothing really all that fancy here. But the phone does look sleek and minimal, which makes it easier to recommend to more people. As far as the specifications go, the Qualcomm Snapdragon 680 4G processor delivers tons of power, and comes paired with 4GB of RAM. You also get 64GB of onboard storage, and a microSD card that supports up to 1TB, which makes expansion simple. In addition, you get a large 6.5-inch screen with a 90Hz refresh rate, along with beautiful colors and great contrast. For the most part, the screen looks good, making it great for media consumption and even games. Battery life is also quite good here, with a 5,000mAh capacity that makes it great for all-day use. The phone also packs a 50MP camera on the rear, and an 8MP camera on the front. There's even a 3.5mm audio jack just in case you want to plug in some headphones. For the most part, you can't go wrong if you're on a budget. The Moto G Play 2024 really delivers on most fronts, making it the ideal phone to pick up right now if you want to get something for cheap. Just be sure to act quickly because, at this price, the deal won't be around for much longer.",
